{
  "texts": [
    "To speed-up computations, we estimated (provably correct) lower bounds of all distances.",
    "We performed exact computations only if the distance bound is at most a chosen distance threshold, which we set to 10, unless stated otherwise.",
    "If the lower bound was above the threshold, we used this bound instead as a distance estimate.",
    "Similarly, if the exact distance was computed and above the threshold, we used the threshold instead.",
    "We used UMAP 29 to visualize the universe of biomolecular structures in a 2-dimensional plot."
  ]
}